modules.description: This module manages dynamic, thread-local ambient state using a heterogeneous map structure. It supports creating typed keys, binding values to keys within a scope, and retrieving values based on keys. Concrete use cases include managing request-specific data in web servers or propagating contextual information across asynchronous workflows without explicit parameter passing.

This module provides operations for managing dynamic, thread-local ambient state using a heterogeneous map structure. It supports creating typed keys, binding values to keys within a scope, and retrieving values based on keys. Concrete use cases include managing request-specific data in web servers or propagating contextual information across asynchronous workflows without explicit parameter passing.
